  "prompt": "Which is the best sports bra?",
  "response": "The \"best\" sports bra can vary widely depending on individual preferences, body types, activity levels, and specific needs. However, here are some highly-rated sports bras that are frequently recommended:\n\n1. **Lululemon Energy Bra** - Known for its comfort and support, it's popular for various activities, from yoga to high-impact workouts.\n\n2. **Nike Alpha Bra** - Offers great support and is ideal for high-impact activities. It features a stylish design and moisture-wicking fabric.\n\n3. **Under Armour Infinity High Sports Bra** - Well-regarded for its comfort and support, it adapts to your movements and is suitable for high-impact sports.\n\n4. **Boden High Support Sports Bra** - Offers excellent support and coverage, making it a favorite among runners and other high-impact athletes.\n\n5. **Brooks Dare Crossback Run Bra** - Specifically designed for runners with a lightweight feel and great support.\n\n6. **Victoria's Secret Sport Incredible Bra** - This option provides good support and style, often recommended for both performance and comfort.\n\n7. **Moving Comfort Juno Sports Bra** - Known for its adjustable features and comfort, it\u2019s great for larger bust sizes and high-impact activities.\n\n8. **Champion The Curvy Sports Bra** - Designed for larger sizes, offering maximum support and comfort.\n\nWhen choosing a sports bra, consider the following factors:\n\n- **Activity Level**: Higher impact sports require more support.\n- **Size and Fit**: Make sure to get the right size; too tight or too loose can be uncomfortable.\n- **Material**: Look for moisture-wicking materials to keep you dry.\n- **Style**: Whether you prefer a racerback, front closure, or traditional, choose one that suits your style.\n\nIt's always best to try on different styles and brands to find what works best for you!",
